<li class="n10"> &lt;<b>@don_armstrong</b>&gt; that concludes the first part of the debate, we'll take a 5 minute break so I can run around the lab here</li>
<li class="n10"> &lt;<b>@don_armstrong</b>&gt; While I'm running around, I'd like to reiterate how the second part of the debate will work; it'll basically be controlled chaos (as opposed to the uncontrolled chaos in the third part)</li>
