<li class="n10"> &lt;<b>@don_armstrong</b>&gt; I will recognize them like the following:</li>
<li class="n10"> &lt;<b>@don_armstrong</b>&gt; recognize don_armstrong </li>
<li class="n10"> &lt;<b>@don_armstrong</b>&gt; they will then have 1.5 minutes to speak (or 5 messagse) whichever is lesser.</li>
